          This is a placeholder homepage. Start building your amazing website here.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-blue-700 bg-opacity-50 rounded-lg p-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 mb-4">
            <strong>Next steps:</strong> Visit the <a href="/admin" class="underline hover:text-white">admin panel</a> to create content, or edit this template at <code class="bg-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">templates/index.twig</code>
